{"tid":1056891,"cid":31,"subCid":0,"title":"嬲/燥底點發洩？","createTime":"2019-03-11T13:33:35.000Z","updateTime":"2019-03-12T16:53:10.000Z","uid":180353,"like":12,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":24,"replies":[{"pid":"de3ee8b9c725e5956623c0d9b78abafed4d1297b","tid":1056891,"uid":180353,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-11T13:33:35.000Z","msg":"點樣可以好快咁調整心態 變返心平氣和？<br />\n好少會嬲 但一好撚嬲就好撚想搵嘢打搵嘢扔<br />\n今朝嬲撚到打撚凹咗兩下部車 屈住屈住好辛苦<br />\n就算有人氹有人安慰係完全冇用 負面緊嬲緊講咩都係唔啱聽<br />\n瞓教同做運動發洩到但又唔係即刻做到同時間長<br />\n點可以做到完全咩都唔會嬲 明明已經咩都麻木冇感覺<br />\n但又好大壓力好煩惱 好撚矛盾<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b6fbf25d8c7d5db45d213d58f485db0abeabe79a","tid":1056891,"uid":61748,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-11T14:40:23.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"72e9ea17ad4ddf796f8ac0a2a5380e3dc3c2551d","tid":1056891,"uid":69452,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-11T14:41:09.000Z","msg":"我老師教，對住個枕頭大叫"},{"pid":"ee6c7ba061586ab4cb5e82d76356bc8fac5777f5","tid":1056891,"uid":94277,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-11T14:53:29.000Z","msg":"試吓一嬲就打飛機"},{"pid":"efd868de5b4015e2c8a92b1a41667ce0bc078bf4","tid":1056891,"uid":29887,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-11T14:55:25.000Z","msg":"搵閪屌"},{"pid":"5a6e205329d795b14c014644ad0bf88a9c993d34","tid":1056891,"uid":238541,"like":8,"dislike":0,"score":8,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-11T14:55:49.000Z","msg":"睇咗 打撚凹咗兩部車 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1ede25d5a18019db6056a107f9d65c1e85a67979","tid":1056891,"uid":127929,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-11T14:56:45.000Z","msg":"打飛機噴米青"},{"pid":"6bac6ca9a403b6f639968d7ae823c3864a1448bb","tid":1056891,"uid":120742,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-03-11T15:08:57.000Z","msg":"即刻只有爆粗。<br />\n但我成日去打拳，望住塊鏡或者沙包，